# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# DEFENSIVE ALLOW-LIST.
# Ignore EVERYTHING by default, then re-include only the files the
# public website needs. This guarantees secrets (KoboToolbox API token
# in *.gs, Google Sheet IDs, spreadsheets, internal docs) can never be
# committed by accident — even files added later stay out unless
# explicitly un-ignored below.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/*

# ── Files the Vercel site needs (the ONLY things published) ──
!.gitignore
!delta-aquaponics-dashboard.html
!vercel.json
